Titolo: Asphalt Xtreme

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Asphalt Xtreme, also known as Asphalt Xtreme: Rally Racing, was an action racing video game, published and developed by Gameloft. It was the second spinoff, and the first off-road racing edition, in the Asphalt series. It was released on 27 October 2016. The game is no longer supported.
Development lasted from August 2015 to September 2017. Development has been terminated after 60 people layoffs and following the Madrid studio shutdown.
From November 2021, Netflix is hosting Asphalt Xtreme servers thanks to contract between Netflix and Gameloft. For login, the user must have Netflix account.

